setWeaponReloadingTime 
Game: ArmA 2: Operation Arrowhead (1.60) 
Description: Sets states and/or makes an action of/on weapon. Reload time is between 
 0 and 1 inclusive, where 1 is 100% of maximum reloading time.  
Syntax:  
 vehicle setWeaponReloadingTime [gunner, weaponName, reloadTime] 
Parameters: 
vehicle: Object 
[gunner, weaponName, reloadTime]: Array 
Return Value: 
 Boolean